# Github workflow_dispatch Event Notification
created: undefined, last updated: 2026-06-02, [Read more](https://www.magicbell.com/workflows/github/workflow-dispatch)

…
```
{
"key": "integration.github.workflow_dispatch",
"steps": [
{
"command": "broadcast",
"input": {
"action_url": "{{payload.repository.html_url}}/actions",
"content": "{{payload.sender.login}} manually triggered {{payload.workflow}} on {{payload.repository.full_name}} ({{payload.ref}}).",
"overrides": {
"providers": {
"slack": {}
}
},
"recipients": [
{
"external_id": "devops-team"
}
],
"title": "Workflow manually triggered"
}
}
]
}
```
